    "detail":"<p><br><strong>Contact Us</strong></p><p>Thank you for your interest in Agrawal Public School! We value your feedback, questions, and inquiries. Here's how you can reach us:</p><p><strong>Customer Support:</strong> For assistance with technical issues, account inquiries, or general support, please email our customer support team at support@Agrawal.com. We strive to respond to all inquiries promptly and provide the assistance you need.</p><p><strong>Partnerships and Collaborations:</strong> If you're interested in partnering with Agrawal Public School or collaborating on wellness initiatives, please reach out to our partnerships team at partnerships@Agrawal.com. We welcome opportunities to work together in promoting health and well-being in the workplace.</p><p><strong>Media and Press Inquiries:</strong> For media inquiries, press releases, or interview requests, please contact our media relations team at media@Agrawal.com. We're happy to provide information, insights, or arrange interviews with our team members.</p><p><strong>Feedback and Suggestions:</strong> Your feedback is invaluable to us as we strive to improve our platform and services. If you have suggestions, ideas, or feedback to share, please email us at feedback@Agrawal.com. We appreciate your input and are dedicated to incorporating it into our ongoing efforts to enhance Agrawal Public School.</p><p><strong>General Inquiries:</strong> For any other inquiries or information not covered above, please feel free to reach out to us at info@Agrawal.com. We're here to assist you and provide any information you may need about Agrawal Public School and our offerings.</p>"
}

